# DFECPIMS
## Digital Forensics Evidence Collection and Process Integrity Management System

---

### Architecture Overview

```
dfecpims/
├── backend/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── models/          # SQLAlchemy ORM models (Module 1 — complete)
│   │   ├── core/            # Database engine, config, security utilities
│   │   ├── api/             # FastAPI route handlers (Modules 2–7)
│   │   ├── services/        # Business logic layer
│   │   └── schemas/         # Pydantic request/response schemas
│   ├── migrations/
│   │   ├── audit_trigger.sql  # INSERT-only trigger — run manually after schema creation
│   │   └── init_schema.py     # Schema creation script (alternative to Alembic)
│   └── requirements.txt
└── frontend/                # React + Tailwind (Module 8)
```

